overview: The day after a crazy night out, besties Alina Lopez and Kitty Carrera decide to spend the evening on the couch with some hot salty popcorn and a sexy movie. These BFFs can't help running their hands all over each other's popping booties as they're popping the corn, then they nibble their salty snack off each other's bodies.
title: Juicy Licks 17
